## How to Run

### 1. Set up MySQL
```bash
mysql -u root -p < server/schema.sql
```

### 2. Configure & seed backend
Edit [server/.env](file:///d:/Learning/Resume/server/.env) with your MySQL password, then:
```bash
cd server
npm run seed
npm start
```

### 3. Start frontend
```bash
cd client
npm run dev
```

### 4. Open
- Website: `http://localhost:5173`
- Admin: `http://localhost:5173/admin/login` (admin / admin123)

